      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 01:20:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪誓言继续掌权，印度股指期货在暴跌后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/india-stock-futures-gain-as-modi-vows-to-hold-power-by-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股指期货上涨，收复了周二遭受的一小部分损失。周二选举结果显示，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党在议会中失去多数席位，需要依靠盟友组建政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/india-stock-futures-gain-as-modi-vows-to-hold-power-by-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 01:11:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲债券跟随美国涨势；印度股票期货上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国劳动力市场降温迹象提振美联储降息预期的影响，亚洲交易中债券跟随美国国债走高。股票则难以找到方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 22:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
